  "remarks": "Reportedly deceased. Passport no.: a) Saudi Arabian passport number K142736 (issued 14 Jul. 2011 in Al-Khafji, Saudi Arabia) b) Saudi Arabian passport number G579315. Was the lead oil and gas division official of Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant (ISIL), listed as Al-Qaida in Iraq (QDe.115), for Al Barakah Governorate, Syrian Arab Repubic, as of May 2015. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2253 (2015) was concluded on 21 Feb. 2019. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link: https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals; Listing: Listed on: 20 Apr. 2016 (amended on 1 May 2019, 21 Jul. 2023)",
